::Firaxis::
       He shakes his head.  "Not entirely, no.  But it doesn't sound good.  
Let's go take down that ship."  He nods confidently.  "If we can take out its 
engines then it'll crash.  Hopefully it won't crash in range of the mountain. 
 If it does we'll have to disable it's weapons.  Permanently."
